  status(success): color: #28a745;
  status(error): color: #dc3545;
  status(warning): color: #ffc107;
  status(muted): color: #888888;
  status(info): color: #d2bc93;
  status(accent): color: #d2bc93;
  
  === light ===
  header:      font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; color: #000000;
  subtitle:    color: #666666; margin-bottom: 10px;
  description: color: #666666; font-size: 9pt;
  tip:         color: #b19145; font-style: italic;
  status(success): color: #28a745;
  status(error): color: #dc3545;
  status(warning): color: #ffc107;
  status(muted): color: #666666;
  status(info): color: #b19145;
  status(accent): color: #b19145;
  
  '''
